    "In terms of system function, the main functions of the TENG tribo-system include sensing and energy supply, so the purpose of its tribological system is energy transfer and information transfer.",
    "The main design purpose of the tribological system is the main basis for judging its output information.Secondly, it is classified from the purpose of tribological research, including condition monitoring, behavior prediction, system optimization, and mechanism analysis.",
